    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是否曾梦想过打造出能点亮别人一天的美丽花束？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Flowers and Favours》是一款温馨放松的花店模拟游戏，在这里你可以亲手制作精美的花束，尝试不同的花材组合，并经营属于你自己的花店。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个属于你的空间，用来创造与放松。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/cfe1d2018d33f927f6eb1cf5aab8f0f1.poster.avif?t=1759131749\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/cfe1d2018d33f927f6eb1cf5aab8f0f1.webm?t=1759131749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/cfe1d2018d33f927f6eb1cf5aab8f0f1.mp4?t=1759131749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>🐰 <strong>遇见可爱的顾客</strong> – 与可爱的角色聊天，他们会用独特的请求激发你的灵感</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/aa4c38fdb9cc7224fc375c37a4e65e54.poster.avif?t=1759131749\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/aa4c38fdb9cc7224fc375c37a4e65e54.webm?t=1759131749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/aa4c38fdb9cc7224fc375c37a4e65e54.mp4?t=1759131749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>释放你的创造力</strong> – 从55种美丽的花材中自由搭配，设计独一无二的花束。尝试不同的形状、颜色和饰品，让每个作品都独具个性</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/f766ef55b0fa2e227d87dbc24a24217a.poster.avif?t=1759131749\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/f766ef55b0fa2e227d87dbc24a24217a.webm?t=1759131749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/f766ef55b0fa2e227d87dbc24a24217a.mp4?t=1759131749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎀 <strong>用完美的包装完成你的杰作</strong> – 从各种温馨的丝带、纸张和花瓶中选择，为花束增添理想的点睛之笔</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/668ffaf02cdc2f6ca964749248ae4b5f.poster.avif?t=1759131749\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/668ffaf02cdc2f6ca964749248ae4b5f.webm?t=1759131749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/668ffaf02cdc2f6ca964749248ae4b5f.mp4?t=1759131749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>参观花卉市场</strong> – 来到黛西的市场，用你辛苦赚取的奖励购买新的花卉和绿植</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/d7e7579fd5790d426d896e820b3ac7aa.poster.avif?t=1759131749\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/d7e7579fd5790d426d896e820b3ac7aa.webm?t=1759131749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269600/extras/d7e7579fd5790d426d896e820b3ac7aa.mp4?t=1759131749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📖 <strong>在相册中欣赏你的作品</strong> – 将你最喜欢的花束保存到特别的相册中，随时重温和珍藏</p>",
